  "display_fullname": "Scrapper Defense Ice Armor Wet Ice",
  "display_help": "When you activate this power, you cover yourself in a thick coating of slick, melting ice. This makes you slippery, leaving you nearly immune to Disorient, Immobilization, Hold, Sleep, Slow and Knockback effects. This power also adds a slight increase to your defense to all attacks. Wet Ice also reduces Cold damage and grants you resistance to Defense DeBuffs.",
